org.sql: SELECT news.* FROM news INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = news.project_id WHERE projects.status <> 9 AND (SELECT 1 AS one FROM enabled_modules AS em WHERE em.project_id = projects.id AND em.name = 'news') IS NOT NULL ORDER BY news.created_on DESC LIMIT 1
